      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single ASTM F1717 offset distance (44 mm) and at ambient laboratory conditions only. Clinical use spans a range of offsets and in vivo temperatures; this single-condition testing limits achievable level to Gradation 2. Noted as a gap; accepted given medium model influence and corroborating analytical sensitivity analysis."
