    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is accepted given medium model influence, medium decision consequence, and corroborating analytical sensitivity analyses demonstrating QoI insensitivity to offset distance variation. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
